  Te7 3 Chiunn<BR>Sim2-mih8 Si7 Kau3-Hoe7 Chi3-siong7 E5 Kang-chok? 
  ChhiaN2 li2 khui Seng3-keng I2-se-kiat 3:17-19, goa2 beh chiong chit-toaN7 Seng3-keng chat e5 kui2-ku3-oe7 kai2-pian3 tam7-poh8. Goa2 ai3 hou7 i sek-hap8 ti7 lan2, hian7-chai7 tui3 17 chat lai5 khai-si2. “Ki-tok-tou5 e5 kang-chok-chia2, goa2 siat-lip8 li2 choe3 I2-sek-liat8 ke siu2-bang7 e5 lang5, sou2-i2 li2 tioh8 thiaN Goa2 e5 chhui3 sou2 kong2 e5, thoe3 Goa2 keng2-kai3 in, Goa2 tui3 phaiN2-lang5 kong2, Li2 tek-khak oe7 si2; na7 li2 bo5 keng2-kai3 i, bo5 eng7 oe7 keng2-kai3 i e5 siN3-mia7, chiu7 hit-e5 phaiN2-lang5 beh si2 ti7 i e5 choe7; chong2-si7 Goa2 beh tui3 li2 e5 chhiu2 tho2 i e5 siN3-mia7, siat-su2 li2 keng2-kai3 phaiN2-lang5, ia7 i bo5 oat8-tng2 li7-khui i e5 phaiN2 sou2 kiaN5 kap i e5 phaiN2-lou7, chiu7 i beh si2 ti7 i e5 choe7, chong2-si7 li2 u7 kiu3 li2 ka-ki7 e5 siN3-mia7.” 
  “Goa2 beh tui3 li2 e5 chhiu2 tho2 i e5 siN3-mia7”, goa2 thak8-tioh8 chit-kui2-ku3 oe7 e5 si5-chun7, goa2 khi2 chhoah khi2-lai5. “Goa2 beh tui3 li2 e5 chhiu2 tho2 i e5 siN3-mia7.” 
  Chit kui2-ni5 lai5 goa2 siu7-tioh8 chit8 ku3 soan-kau3 phiau-gu2 e5 kam2-tong7. Hian7-chai7 goa2 beh ka7 li2 kong2 chit-e5, che si7 goa2 khoaN3 choe3 pi2 ki5-thaN e5 su7 koh khah u7 i3-gi7 e5, chiu7-si7 kong2: “Kau3-hoe7 chi3-siong7 e5 kang-chok, chiu7-si7 tui3 choan5 se3-kai3 thoan5 hok-im”, Goa2 choan5-sim siong-sin3 chit-e5 phiau-gu2, Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 kau3-hoe7 choe3 tiong7-iau3 e5 kang-chok chiu7-si7 tui3 se3-kai3 thoan5 hok-im. 
  SE3-KAI3 
  Goa2 tui3 chit-e5 phiau-gu2 tiong ai3 theh8 3 ku3 oe7 lai5, jian5-au7 chit8-ku3 chit8-ku3 ka7 i kiong5-tiau. Te7-it, goa2 ai3 theh8 choe3-au7 e5 chit8-ku3 oe7, chiu7-si7 “Se3-kai3” chit ku3. Siong7-te3 chin thiaN3 se3-kai3, chiu7 chiong I e5 tok8-seN-kiaN2 siuN2-su3 hou7 se3-kai3. Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 si2, si7 ui7-tioh8 se3-kai3, Siong7-te3 sou2 teh siuN7 e5, chiu7-si7 se3-kai3. I ia7 ai3 lan2 tioh8 u7 chit khoan2 e5 sim. 
  Lan2 choe7-choe7 lang5 teh siu2-bang7, chha-put-to long2 si7 chi2-u7 siu2 chit8 sio2 pou7-hun7 na7-tiaN7. Lan2 chi2-u7 khoaN3-kiN3 ka-ki7 e5 thoan5-the2, ka-ki7 e5 hiong-chhoan a2-si7 siaN5-tin3, long2 bo5 teh koan-sim ki5-thaN e5 sou2-chai7. U7 choe7-choe7 lang5 chi2-u7 ui7-tioh8 in ka-ki7 e5 kau3-hoe7 teh siuN7 na7-tiaN7, tui3 ki5-thaN e5 kau3-hoe7 sou2 teh choe3 e5 su7 long2 bo5 u7 tam7-poh8 e5 koan-sim. Chong2-si7 u7 e5 lang5, u7 khah toa7 e5 iN7-siong7, in khoaN3-kiN3 sou2 toa3 e5 choan5-chhi7 a2-si7 choan5-seng2, in chin hoaN-hi2 hian3 in e5 kim-chiN5 lai5 chun2-pi7 choan5-chhi7, choan5-seng2 e5 pou3-to7 tai7-hoe7. In e5 siu2-bang7 thang kong2, ia7 si7 chi2-u7 chit8 sio2 pou7-hun7 na7-tiaN7, in tek-khak bo5 koan-sim in sou2 toa3 e5 chhi7, seng2, i2-goa7 e5 toe7-hng. Na7-si7 iau2 u7 chit8-koa2 lang5 in u7 koh khah toa7 e5 iN7-siong7, in koan-sim ti7 choan5-kok, in hoaN-hi2 chin7 in e5 lek8-liong7 teh chun2-pi7 choan5-kok pou3-to7 e5 kang-chok. Chong2-si7 chiah-e5 lang5 ia7 chi2-u7 si7 chit8-pou7-hun7 e5 koan-sim na7-tiaN7, in tek-khak bo5 koan-sim ti7 pat8 e5 kok-ka. U7 lang5 u7 koh khah toa7 e5 iN7-siong7, in hoaN-hi2 ui7-tioh8 in sou2 toa3 e5 tai7-liok8 lai5 chun2-pi7 it-chhe3 thoan5-to7 e5 kang-chok, chiah-e5 lang5 e5 siu2-bang7 ia7 si7 chi2 u7 kiok8-pou7-tek e5, in-ui7 in bo5 koan-sim ti7 in e5 tai7-liok8 i2-goa7 e5 sou2-chai7. Tan3-si7 ia7 u7 lang5 si7 koan-sim ti7 choan5 se3-kai3 e5 su7, in koan-sim Au-chiu, A-chiu, Lam5-pak Bi2-chiu, choe7-choe7 hai2-su7, in u7 Siong7-te3 e5 khoaN3-hoat, chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3 ai3 lan2 tak8-lang5 tioh8 u7 e5 iN7-siong7. 
  SiaN2-su7 hiah-nih8 choe7 e5 lang5 chi2-u7 siu2-bang7 chit8-sio2 pou7-hun7 nih? Siong7-te3 kan-taN koan-sim ng5-cheng2-lang5 bo5 koan-sim ti7 ou-lang5 mah? Siong7-te3 kan-taN koan-sim peh8-lang5 chiu7 bo5 koan-sim ti7 hiah-e5 chhiah-sek e5 lang5 mah? Si7 lan2 e5 bak8-chiu bo5 khoaN3 tioh8 choan5 se3-kai3, a2-si7 kin7-si7 beh? Goa2 beh li7-khui Ge5-be2-ka to2-su7 chiuN7 hui-ki e5 si5-chun7, goa2 chi2-u7 khoaN3-kiN3 hu7-kin7 e5 kong-keng2 na7-tiaN7. Jian5-au7 hui-ki pe khi2-lai5 chiuN7 kau3 koan5 e5 sou2-chai7, hit-e5 goa2 u7 khoaN3-kiN3 chin choe7 e5 chhan5-hng5 kap chhu3-theh8. Chong2-si7 goan2 peh-chiuN7 koh khah koan5 e5 si5-chun7, chiu7 thang khoaN3 tioh8 ti7 hng7-hng7 e5 soaN-kok kap choe7-choe7 soaN. Choe3-au7 goan2 u7 khoaN3-kiN3 Ge5-be2-ka to2-su7 choan5-pou7 lah, i chhin-chhiuN7 chit8-liap8 e5 po2-chioh8 ti7 Ka-lek-pi2 hai2 e5 tiong-ng. Siat-su2 goan2 na7 oe7 thang chiuN7 koh khah koan5, goan2 it-teng7 oe7 thang khoaN3-tioh8 Se-in3-tou7 sou2 u7 e5 to2-su7 lah. 
  Siong7-te3 tui3 I hia, siang7-si5 oe7 thang khoaN3-tioh8 choan5 se3-kai3 mui2 chit8 e5 kok-ka, tai7-liok8 kap to2-su7. Siat-su2 lan2 na7 li7-khui lan2 e5 sou2-chai7 kau3 koaiN5-koaiN5 e5 ui7, lan2 chiu7 oe7 thang khoaN3-kiN3 Ia5-sou sou2 khoaN3-tioh8 e5 se3-kai3. Chong2-si7 ti7 lan2 tiong-kan, u7 lang5 m7-bat chhut-goa7, ia7 m7-bat thiaN lu2-heng5-ka sou2 kong2 e5 su7, m7-bat hak8-sip8 toe7-li2, koan-he7 li7-khui lan2 chin hng7 e5 sou2-chai7 e5 su7 long2 bo5 sim2-mih8 chai-iaN2. 
  SiaN2-su7 lan2 ka-ki7 siuN7 lan2 si7 pi2 se3-kai3 pat8 sou2-chai7 e5 lang5 koh khah tiong7-iau3 neh? Goa2 kau3 tak8 sou2-chai7, siong5-siong5 thiaN-kiN3 chit-khoan2 e5 oe7. Goa2 ti7 Eng-kok e5 si5, u7 thiaN-kiN3 hia e5 lang5 kong2, “Goan2 si7 chia e5 peh-siN3”. Goa2 ti7 O3-tai7-li7-a, Niu2-se-lan5 e5 si5 ia7 thiaN-kiN3 hia e5 lang5 kong2, “Goan2 si7 chia e5 peh-siN3”, Goa2 khi3 Bi2-kok, ia7 ti7 tak8 sou2-chai7 thiaN-kiN3, “Goan2 si7 chia e5 peh-siN3”. U7 chit8-pai2 goa2 kau3 ti7 Thai3-peng5-iuN5 chit8 e5 sio2-to2, hia e5 thou2-lang5 ia7 teh kong2, “Goan2 si7 chia e5 peh-siN3.” In siong5-siong5 ka7 goa2 kong2, “Lin2 Bi2-kok lang5, siaN2-su7 toa3 ti7 hiah-nih hng7, li7-khui bun5-beng5, kau3 ti7 pian-kai3 e5 sou2-chai7 nih? SiaN2-su7 lin2 bo5 beh tiam3 ti7 khah kin7 se3-kai3 tiong-sim e5 sou2-chai7 nih?” In e5 i3-su3 si7 ai3 kong2, Eng-kok lang5 kap Bi2-kok lang5 si7 tiam3 ti7 chin hng7 e5 sou2-chai7, li7-khui bun5-beng5 e5 pian-kai3 hit peng5. Hiah-e5 thou2-lang5 sui-jian5 toa3 ti7 Thai3-peng5-iuN5 soe3-soe3 e5 to2-su7, chong2-si7 in siuN7, sou2 toa3 e5 sou2-chai7 si7 se3-kai3 e5 tiong-sim. TaN bun7-te5 si7 in sou2 koan-sim e5 chi2-u7 in ka-ki7 e5 sou2-chai7 na7-tiaN7, in long2 bo5 u7 chit8 e5 se3-kai3 e5 iN7-siong7, in siuN7 in si7 se3-kai3 choe3 te7-it iau3-kin2 e5 peh-siN3. 
  SiaN2-su7 lan2 oe7 an2-ni siuN7? Kiam2-chhai2 si7 in-ui7 lan2 teh siuN7, lan2 si7 choan5 se3-kai3 jin5-sou3 te7-it choe7 e5. Goa2 chin kiaN ti7 lan2 tiong-kan iau2 u7 lang5 bo5 beng5-pek8 ti7 se3-kai3 iau2 u7 ki5-thaN kok-ka e5 peh-siN3 si7 jin5-sou3 pi2 lan2 koh khah choe7, lan2 m7 si7 hai2-piN soa-pou tiong chi2-u7 chit8-liap8 e5 sio2 iN5-chioh8. 
  Goa2 ti7 In3-ni5 e5 si5, u7 che7 chhia koe3 Jia2-oa to2-su7, goa2 eng7 12 tiam2-cheng, tui3 tang-peng5 kau3 sai-peng5, koh eng7 4 tiam2-cheng tui3 lam5 kau3 pak. Chong2-si7 goa2 na7 ka7 li2 kong2, Jia2-oa chit-e5 to2-su7 si7 choan5 se3-kai3 jin5-khau2 te7-it choe7, li2 kiam2 beh sin3? Ti7 hit-e5 sio2-sio2 e5 to2 nih8 u7 5 chheng-ban7 e5 jin5-khau2, goa2 thang chiong 15 e5 Jia2-oa to2 he7 ti7 Ka-na2-tai7, iau2 oe7 koh chhun choe7-choe7 sou2-chai7, chong2-si7 Jia2-oa to2 e5 jin5-khau2 kap Bi2-kok pi2 khi2-lai5, si7 chi2-u7 Bi2-kok jin5-khau2 3 hun7 e5 chit8-hun7. Siat-su2 Siong7-te3 na7 koan-sim jin5-khau2 e5 che7-chio2, an2-ni Siong7-te3 tek-khak khah koan-sim Jia2-oa chiah tioh8! Ti7 Ka-na2-tai7 e5 leng2-thou2 lau5 chi2-u7 1800 ban7 e5 peh-siN3 na7-tiaN7, na7 kap Jia2-oa pi2-kau3, sit8-chai7 chin chio2. 
  Siong7-te3 na7 kan-ta koan-sim ti7 sou3-ji7, I it-teng7 koan-sim Bi2-kok khah iaN5-keo3 Jia2-oa, in-ui7 Jia2-oa e5 jin5-khau2 5000 ban7, Bi2-kok e5 jin5-khau2 1 ek 8000 ban7. I it-teng7 khah koan-sim Sou-ngou5 iaN5-koe3 Bi2-kok, in-ui7 Bi2-kok e5 jin5-khau2 si7 1 ek 8000 ban7, na7-si7 Sou-ngou5 e5 jin5-khau2 2 ek. Sou-ngou5 si7 peh8-lang5 e5 se3-kai3 tiong jin5-khau2 te7 it che7 e5 kok-ka. Koh kong2 chit8-pian3, Siong7-te3 na7 kan-ta chhu3-bi7 ti7 sou3-bak8, I it-teng7 khah koan-sim In3-tou7 iaN5-koe3 Sou-ngou5, in-ui7 Sou-ngou5 e5 jin5-khau2 2 ek, na7-si7 In3-tou7 e5 jin5-khau2 u7 4 ek, tu2-tu2 si7 Sou-ngou5 e5 2 poe7. chong2-si7 choe3-au7 chit8-pai2 lai5 kong2, siat-su2 Siong7-te3 na7 tui3 sou3-bak8 chin-chiaN3 chhu3-bi7, I it-teng7 koh khah koan-sim ti7 Tiong-kok iaN5-koe3 In3-tou7, in-ui7 In3-tou7 e5 jin5-khau2 4 ek, na7-si7 Tiong-kok e5 jin5-khau2 u7 7 ek. Tiong-kok ti7 se3-kai3 thang kong2 choe3 toa7 e5 kok-ka, ti7 se3-kai3 u7 4 e5 eN-a2 chhut-si3, ki5-tiong u7 chit8 e5 si7 Tiong-kok lang5. Sou2-i2 u7 lang5 kong2: “Siong7-te3 it-teng7 khah thiaN3 Tiong-kok, in-ui7 I chhong3-cho7 hiah-nih choe7 e5 Tiong-kok lang5.” 
  Lun7 kau3 goa2 e5 kok-ka Ka-na2-tai7, ti7 toe7-tou5 put-ko3 chiam3 chit8-sut-sut-a2 na7-tiaN7. Siat-su2 Tai7-se-iuN5 kap Thai3-peng5-iuN5 e5 hai2-chui2, na7 ti7 chit8-me5 e5 tiong-kan tiong3 khi2-lai5, im-moa2 choan5-pou7 e5 Ka-na2-tai7, goa2 siong-sin3 ti7 keh-jit8 cha2-khi2, Bi2-kok e5 po3-choa2 it-teng7 u7 chin choe7 po3 kong2, “Cha-me5 Ka-na2-tai7 i2-keng tui3 se3-kai3 e5 tiong-kan siau-biat8 lah.” Na7 eng7 sou3-bak8 lai5 sng3, lan2 boe7-tang3 sng3 choe3 sim2-mih8. Lan2 ki3-jian5 si7 an2-ni, siaN2-su7 ka-ki7 teh siuN7, “goan2 si7 chia e5 peh-siN3” neh? SiaN2-su7 siuN7 lan2 si7 pi2 se3-kai3 ki5-thaN sou2-chai7 e5 lang5 koh khah iau3-kin2 nih? SiaN2-su7 Siong7-te3 it-teng7 tioh8 pi2 pat8-lang5 khah koan-sim lan2 nih? I ai3 lan2 u7 se3-kai3 e5 iN7-siong7, an2-ni lan2 chiu7 thang ui7-tioh8 choan5 se3-kai3 lai5 choe3 thoan5 hok-im e5 kang-chok. Ki-tok si7 ui7-tioh8 se3-kai3 lai5 si2 e5, lan2 na7 u7 tui3 choan5 se3-kai3 thoan5-to7 e5 iN7-siong7, lan2 chiu7 oe7 thang khoaN3-kiN3, I sou2 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 se3-kai3 lah. 
  CHI3-SIONG7 
  Hian7-tai7 lan2 lai5 khoaN3 phiau-gu2 leng7-goa7 chit8-ku3, chiu7-si7 “Chi3-siong7”. Chit ku3 oe7 “Kau3-hoe7 chi3-siong7 e5 kang-chok chiu7-si7 tui3 se3-kai3 thoan5 hok-im.” 
  Tui3 se3-kai3 e5 thoan5-to7 na7-si7 lan2 choe3 tiong7-iau3 e5 kang-chok, soan-kau3 hoe7-gi7 teh khui-hoe7 e5 si5, lan2 eng-kai tioh8 pang3-sak it-chhe3, khi3 chham-ka mui2 chit8 e5 hoe7-gi7. Na7 bo5, lan2 chiu7-si7 bo5 liah8 chit-e5 choe3 te7-it, goa2 siong-sin3 chit-e5 su7 si7 pi2 it-chhe3 koh khah iau3-kin2 e5, tioh8 eng7 lan2 e5 heng5-tong7 lai5 piau2-si7, lan2 si7 chiong thoan5-to7 choe3 iau3-kin2 e5. 
  Te7 2 tiam2, siat-su2 lan2 na7 chiong se3-kai3 e5 thoan5-to7 choe3 te7-it, an2-ni lan2 tioh8 chip8-tiong lan2 e5 cheng-sin5, hong7-hian3 ti7 kok-goa7 e5 thoan5-to7, hou7 ki5-thaN bo5 u7 iN7-siong7 e5 lang5 khi3 koan-sim ki5-thaN e5 tai7-chi3. Hiah-e5 liah8 kok-lai7 e5 kang-chok thang choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 lang5, si5-siong5 u7 chin-choe7 kang-chok thang choe3. Chong2-si7 tui3 kou2-cha2 kau3 taN chin chio2 lang5 koan-sim ti7 kau3-hoe7 chi3-siong7 e5 kang-chok. 
  Siat-su2 lan2 na7 liah8 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 choe3 te7-it, lan2 eng-kai tioh8 pi2 ki5-thaN e5 su7 koh khah toa7 kong3-hian3 ti7 kok-goa7 e5 thoan5-to7 chiah tioh8. ChhiaN2 mng7, li2 na7-si7 seng-li2 lang5 u7 khah choe7 chiN5, li2 beh tau5-chu ti7 ta2-loh8? Tong-jian5 si7 beh tau5-chu ti7 te7-it iau3-kin2 e5 seng-li2. In-ui7 li2 ng3-bang7 beh hoat-tian2 li2 e5 seng-li2 te7-it iau3-kin2 e5 pou7-hun7. Tui3 goa7-kok e5 thoan5-to7 eng-kai ia7 tioh8 an2-ni. Tui3 se3-kai3 thoan5-to7 si7 kau3-hoe7 choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 kang-chok, lan2 eng-kai tioh8 chiong lan2 e5 chiN5, tau5-chu ti7 chit-e5 choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 pou7-hun7. Na7 bo5, lan2 chiu7 m7-si7 chiong goa7-kok thoan5-to7 choe3 te7-it, in-ui7 lan2 bo5 sin3 che si7 kau3-hoe7 chi3-siong7 e5 kang-chok. Goa2 kam2-kak chin chio2 bok8-su, chin chiaN3 teh sin3 tui3 se3-kai3 thoan5-to7 si7 in choe3 tiong7-iau3 e5 kang-chok. 
  Chit hang7 su7 goa2 ai3 kong2: “Mui2 chit8-keng kau3-hoe7, eng7 ti7 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 hui3-iong7 tioh8 pi2 eng7 ti7 ka-ki7 e5 kau3-hoe7 koh khah choe7 chiah tioh8. Che si7 chin u7 hap8-li2 e5, lan2 na7 siong-sin3, tui3 se3-kai3 thoan5-to7 choe3 te7-it, an2-ni lan2 eng-kai tioh8 tau5-chu ti7 goa7-kok e5 thoan5-to7, pi2 eng7 ti7 lan2 ka-ki7 e5 kau3-hoe7 e5 hui3-iong7 koh khah che7. 
  Ku7-ni5 chiaN-geh8 tui3 goa2 kau3-hoe7 cha-siau3 e5 lang5, goa2 mng7 2 e5 bun7-te5: te7-it, “Ku7-ni5 lan2 ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 u7 eng7 joa7-choe7 chiN5?” In tiau-cha siau3-phou7 ka7 goa2 in3 kong2, “Su2-bit8-su phok-su7, li2 ku7-ni5 u7 su2-iong7 4 ban7 5 chheng-khou ti7 li2 pun2 kau3-hoe7 e5 kang-chok”. Jian5-au7, goa2 chiu7 mng7 te7-ji7 e5 bun7-te5 kong2, “Lan2 u7 eng7 joa7-choe7 ti7 goa7-kok e5 thoan5-to7?” “Ku7-ni5 li2 u7 eng7 29 ban7 8 chheng-khou ti7 goa7-kok e5 thoan5-to7”. Goa2 kong2, “Chin ho2”, tan3-si7 lin2 kiam2 bo5 khoaN3 m7 tioh8? Si7 lan2 ka-ki7 eng7 29 ban7 8 chheng-khou, ia7 tui3 goa7-kok chiah eng7 4 ban7 5 chheng-khou nih? In kong2, “M7 si7, goan2 bo5 m7-tioh8, li2 eng7 29 ban7 8 chheng-khou ti7 goa7-kok, eng7 4 ban7 5 chheng khou ti7 ka-ki7 e5 kau3-hoe7”. Goa2 in3 kong2, “Chin ho2 lah, an2-ni chiah eng-kai, tioh8 siong5-siong5 an2-ni chiah ho2”. Siat-su2 Bin5-chiong3 kau3-hoe7 e5 tiong2-chip na7 lai5 tui3 goa2 kong2, “Eng7 ti7 pun2 kau3-hoe7 e5 hui3-iong7, eng-kai tioh8 pi2 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 koh khah choe7”. An2-ni in tek-khak oe7 liam5-piN chiap-tioh8 goa2 e5 si5-chit-su, chi2-u7 oe7-hiau2 ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 eng7 choe7-choe7 chiN5, ia7 m7 goan7-i3 tui3 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 eng7 khah choe7 chiN5 e5 kau3-hoe7, goa2 bo5 ai3 choe3 in e5 bok8-su. Goa2 chin hoaN-hi2 goan2 chi2-u7 ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 eng7 4 ban7 5 chheng khou, ia7 ti7 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 eng7 29 ban7 8 chheng khou. 
  Sou3-ni5 cheng5 goa2 khai-si2 chhong3-siat Bin5-chiong3 kau3-hoe7 e5 si5, goa2 u7 thiaN-tioh8 choe7-choe7 hang7 su7, tan3-si7 u7 chit8-hang7 lang5 bo5 ka7 goa2 kong2. Kau3 ti7 le2-pai3-jit8, goa2 beh khai-si2 thau5 chit8-pai2 kang2-to7 e5 si5, koe3-ke3 bin7 iu-chhiu5 lai5 tui3 goa2 kong2, “Su2-bit8-su phok-su7, tu5-liau2 chit8-hang7 i2-goa7, goan2 i2-keng chiong kau3-hoe7 it-chhe3 e5 su7 long2 ka7 li2 kong2 lah.” Goa2 theng3-hau7 i tau3-ti2 beh kong2 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3. Theng5 chit8-si5-a2 i chiu7 kong2: “Chit keng kau3-hoe7 u7 hu7-che3, goan2 u7 chit8-koa2 eng-kai tioh8 lap8 e5 chiN5, be7-tang3 lap8, ti7 koe3-ke3 e5 chhiu2 long2 bo5 chiN5”. I kong2 liau2-au7 it-tit8 khoaN3 goa2, chhin-chhiuN7 teh ng3-bang7 goa2 oe7 tui3 lak-te7-a2 theh8 chiN5, tui3 i kong2, “theh8 chiah-e5 chiN5 khi3 heng5 che3.” 
  Na7-si7 goa2 bo5 an2-ni choe3, hoan2-tng2 oat8-tng2-sin, kiaN5 khi3 kang2-tai5. Chong2-si7 goa2 teh kiaN5 e5 si5, ki5-to2 kong2, “Chu2 ah, goa2 beh tui3 chit8 e5 su7 lai5 chai-iaN2 Seng3-keng lai7-bin7 e5 i3-gi7.” Goa2 siuN7 kau3 Seng3-keng kong2, “Lin2 tioh8 tai7-seng kiu5 I e5 kok (ui7-tioh8 beh khok-tiong Siong7-te3 e5 kok kau3 choan5 se3-kai3), kap I e5 gi7, chiu7 chiah-e5 mih8 long2 beh soa3 hou7 lin2”. Hit jit8 goa2 ui7-tioh8 kok-goa7 e5 thoan5-to7 lai5 kang2-to7. 
  Le2-pai3-jit8 am3 lah, si7 goa2 ti7 hia kang2-to7 e5 thau5 chit8 e5 le2-pai3-jit8, goa2 eng-kai tioh8 thoan5 Hok-im e5 to7-li2, chong2-si7 goa2 kam2-kak tioh8 kong2 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 to7-li2, sou2-i2 goa2 chiu7 kong2 chit toe5-bak8. Hit me5 goa2 chhiaN2 hoe7-chiong3 ti7 chit le2-pai3 tiong tak8-me5 long2 lai5, in ko2-jian5 long2-chong2 lai5 le2-pai3, in koh-chai3 tui3 goa2 thiaN-tioh8 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 to7-li2. Pai3-ji7 in iah8 tui3 goa2 thiaN-tioh8 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 to7-li2, pai3-saN in koh-chai3 thiaN-tioh8 leng7-goa7 chit8 phiN koan-he7 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 to7-li2, pai3-si3 am3 goa2 iu5-koh kong2 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 to7-li2. Pai3-gou7 thiaN-chiong3 cheng-ka, kiam2-chhai2 si7 ui7-tioh8 hi-ki5 e5 in-toaN lai5 e5, chong2-si7 in sou2 thiaN-tioh8 e5 iu5-goan5 si7 chit8-phiN koan-he7 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 to7-li2. 
  Goa2 teh siuN7 in tek-khak saN-kap teh kong2, “Goan2 chit-ui7 sin bok8-su, goan2 chin boe7 liau2-kai2 i, chhin-chhiuN7 tu5-khi3 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 i2-goa7 bo5 u7 sim2-mih8 to7-li2 e5 khoan2. TaN te7 2 le2-pai3-jit8 teh beh kau3 lah, kiam2-chhai2 i beh chin chiaN3 khai-si2 kang2-to7.” 
  Te7 2 le2-pai3-jit8 kau3 lah, goa2 oe7-ki3-tit hit jit8 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 cha7-jit8 chit8-poaN-iuN7, ti7 cha2-khi2-si5 e5 le2-pai3, goa2 po3-ko3 kong2: “Kin-a2-jit8 lan2 beh ku2-heng5 3 pai2 e5 le2-pai3, ia7 beh ui7-tioh8 kok-goa7 thoan5-to7 hong7-hian3 3 pai3, thau5 chit8-pai3 si7 cha2-khi2, te7 2 pai3 si7 e7-pou, te7 3 pai2 si7 e7-am3”. U7 chit8-pou7-hun7 e5 lang5 chhin-chhiuN7 tioh8-kiaN e5 khoan2 teh khoaN3 goa2, na7-si7 goa2 chiu7 khai-si2 goa2 e5 kang-chok lah. Goa2 tit-tioh8 chit8 e5 soan-kau3-su e5 pang-chan7 ke3-oe7 beh khui soan-kau3-su hoe7-gi7. Koat-teng7 an2-ni choe3, hit cha2-khi2 goa2 kong2 koan-he7 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 to7-li2, ia7 chhiaN2 hoe7-chiong3 tioh8 ui7-tioh8 kok-goa7 thoan5-to7 lai5 hong7-hian3. Ha7-ngou2 am3-si5 e5 chu7-hoe7 long2 saN-tang5, goa2 ti7 chia long2 bo5 kong2 kau3 u7 ui7-tioh8 pun2 kau3-hoe7 lai5 hong7-hian3. Goa2 ia7 chiong sou2 hong7-hian3 e5 cho3 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 e5 lou7-eng7. Na7 chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni koh ke3-siok8 loh8-khi3, oe7 chaiN2-iuN7. 
  In piN3-choe3 chin koan-sim kok-goa7 thoan5-to7, chham-ka chu7-hoe7 e5 lang5-giah8 jit8-jit8 ke-thiN. Choe7-choe7 leng5-hun5 tit-kiu3, kau3-hoe7 lai7-bin7 e5 che7-ui7 chin kin2 chiu7 che7 moa2, bo5 ku2 in ia7 tit-tioh8 iN7-siong7, sou2-i2 in chiu7 khai-si2 hong7-hian3, hong7-hian3 in koe3-khi3 sou2 m7-bat hong7-hian3 e5. Ti7 kui2 le2-pai3 tiong, chin kin2 chiu7 chiong kau3-hoe7 e5 che3-bu7 long2 heng5 chheng-chhou2, koh tui3 hit jit8 kau3 kin-a2-jit8, ti7 goan2 e5 kang-chok tiong, long2 m7-bat koh khoaN3-kiN3 hu7-che3 chit-e5 ji7, goan2 chai-iaN2 goan2 chiong eng-kai he7 ti7 te7-it e5 he7 ti7 te7-it e5 si5, Siong7-te3 pun2-sin chiu7 ka-ki7 kang-chok. 
  It-poaN e5 kau3-hoe7 sou2 tu2-tioh8 e5 khun3-lan5, chiu7-si7 chiong chhia he7 ti7 be2 e5 thau5-cheng5, jian5-au7 bok8-su siu7 beng7 khui-chhia, che7 ti7 i e5 ui7 sai2-chhia. Chong2-si7 lan2 na7 chiap-lap8 Siong7-te3 e5 ke3-oe7, lan2 chiu7 chin iong5-iN7 khoaN3 beh khi3 ta2-loh8 chiu7 khi3 ta2-loh8, chhia chiu7 chin ho2 sai2 lah. Sou2-i2 tai7-seng tioh8 lou2-lek8 chiong Siong7-te3 kok khong3-khoah kau3 choan5 se3-kai3, jian5-au7 Siong7-te3 chiu7 oe7 chiong it-chhe3 e5 khiam3-kheh siuN2-su3 lan2, in-ui7 Siong7-te3 e5 ke3-oe7 tek-khak boe7 oe7 sit-pai7. 
  Siat-su2 goa2 na7 siu7 pheng3-chhiaN2 kau3 ti7 leng7-goa7 chit8-keng kau3-hoe7, ia7 hit keng kau3-hoe7 iu5-goan5 u7 hu7-che3, goa2 tek-khak oe7 chiau3 i2-cheng5 e5 choe3-hoat khi3 choe3. Goa2 tek-khak beh khui chit8 e5 toa7 e5 soan-kau3-su hoe7-gi7, au7-lai5 kiu5 Siong7-te3 lai5 koan-sim toe7-hng e5 che3-bu7. Siong7-te3 tek-khak boe7 kou-hu7 goa2. Sou2-i2 lan2 eng-kai tioh8 choe3 e5, chiu7-si7 tioh8 tai7-seng khi3 choe3, jian5-au7 se3-ji7 khoaN3 Siong7-te3 e5 kang-chok. 
  KAU3-HOE7 
  Te7 3 ku3 goa2 sou2 beh kiong5-tiau e5 chiu7-si7 “Kau3-hoe7” chit ku3 oe7. “Kau3-hoe7 chi3-siong7 e5 kang-chok chiu7-si7 tui3 se3-kai3 thoan5 hok-im”, goa2 sou2 teh kong2 e5 kau3-hoe7 chiu7-si7 choan5-pou7 e5 kau3-hoe7. Phi3-ju7 lai5 kong2, ti7 Bin5-chiong3 kau3-hoe7 bo5 Lu2-soan-to7-hoe7. Goan2 koat-teng7 bo5 ai3 chit khoan2 e5 chou-chit, goa2 m7-si7 hoan2-tui3 chit khoan2 e5 thoan5-the2, goa2 beh ui7-tioh8 mui2 chit8 e5 lu2-soan e5 thoan5-the2 chin kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3. U7 si5 soan-kau3 e5 kng si7 tui3 lu2-soan thoan5-the2 hoat-chhut. Chong2-si7 goa2 ai3 eng7 2 hun-cheng ku2 e5 si5-kan chiu7 beh hou7 li2 beng5-pek8, chit8-khoan2 e5 chou-chit tui3 goan2 si7 bo5 pit-iau3 e5. 
  Ka2-su2 goa2 ti7 lu2-soan e5 chu7-hoe7, tui3 in kong2, “Hian7-chai7 lin2 beh chiaN5 chit8 e5 lu2-soan-kau3-su-thoan5, lin2 sou2 tioh8 choe3 e5 kang-chok chiu7-si7 chiong hok-im thoan5 kau3 choan5 se3-kai3, che si7 lin2 tak8 e5 sou2 tioh8 choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 kang-chok”. Na7 an2-ni, i2-au7 goa2 beh tui3 mui2 chit8 lang5, a2-si7 kau3-hoe7 lai7 ki5-thaN chou2-chit kong2-oe7 e5 si5 m7 chai beh an2-choaN2 kong2? Hit si5 goa2 kiam2-chhai2 tioh8 kong2 an2-ni “Chit-e5 m7 si7 kau3-hoe7 lai7 choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 kang-chok, put-ko3 si7 chit8 sio2 pou7-hun7 e5 su7, si7 kau3-hoe7 kang-chok chin choe7 tiong e5 chit8 pou7-hun7 na7-tiaN7, hou7 hiah-e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 khi3 koan-sim chiu7 ho2, in oe7 koan-sim ti7 se3-kai3 thoan5-to7, sou2 chhun e5 lan2,----chiu7-si7 lan2 chiah-e5 ta-pou-lang5----lan2 tioh8 choe3 chin-sit8 u7 ke3-tat8 lan2 ta-pou-lang5 sou2 tioh8 choe3 e5 su7.” 
  Bo5! Mui2 chit8 lang5 ti7 goa2 e5 kau3-hoe7, long2 si7 soan-kau3-su hoe7 e5 chit8 hun7-chu2. Goa2 chin ki5-thai7, 80 mia5 a2-si7 koh khah choe7 e5 seng3-koa-tui7-oan5, choan5-pou7 long2 u7 chiap-lap8 in e5 chek-jim7, sou2 u7 e5 tiuN2-lo2, chip-su7, hoe7-iu2, mui2 chit8 e5 chiau-thai7-oan5, mui2 chit8 e5 Chu2-jit8-oh8 kau3-oan5, a2-si7 su7-bu7-oan5, mui2 chit8 e5 ta-pou gin2-na2 kap cha-bou2 gin2-na2 long2 tioh8 kong3-hian3 ti7 kok-goa7 thoan5-to7. Goa2 bo5 ai3 pe7-bu2 hong7-hian3 in kiaN2-ji5, goan2 ai3 ka3-si7 gin2-na2 tioh8 hong7-hian3 in ka-ki7, tui3 in 5 hoe3 a2-si7 6 hoe3 e5 si5 in tit-tioh8 chit-e5 ka3-si7, kau3 ti7 tiong2-toa7 e5 si5, m7-bian2 koh tui3 pat8-lang5 lai5 hak8-sip8 chaiN2-iuN7 lai5 hong7-hian3, a2-si7 pang-chan7 lang5. 
  Chit-e5 kang-chok si7 pi2 sim2-mih8 chou2-chit koh khah iau3-kin2, in-ui7 che si7 siok8 ti7 choan5-pou7 kau3-hoe7. Mui2 chit8 lang5 long2 tit-tioh8 iN7-siong7 e5 si5, chiu7 long2 oe7 khai-si2 kang-chok. Lan2 e5 phiau-gu2 si7, “mui2 chit8 e5 Ki-tok-tou5 long2 si7 soan-kau3-su”. Che chiu7-si7 choan5 kau3-hoe7 e5 kang-chok. 
  SI7 CHAINN2-IUNN7 CHOE3-CHIANN5 E5? 
  Bo5-lun7 goa2 khi3 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7, lang5 long2 mng7 goa2 chit-e5 bun7-te5. “Li2 si7 chaiN2-iuN7 lai5 tit-tioh8 chit khoan2 e5 hong7-hian3? Hiah-e5 chiN5 si7 tui3 ta2-loh8 lai5 e5? Li2 e5 kau3-hoe7 u7 chin choe7 pah-ban7 pu3-ong mah?” Ka-na2-tai7 Thian-chu2-kau3 sin-bun5 e5 phian-chip, khoaN3-tioh8 goan2 e5 po3-ko3-pio2 sou2 kam2-kak e5, i sia2-phoe ka7 goa2 mng7 kong2, “Li2 e5 kau3-hoe7 u7 chin choe7 pah-ban7 pu3-ong mah?” Goa2 ka7 i in3-kong2: “Bo5” i chin tioh8-kiaN, au7-lai5 i ti7 Thian-chu2-kau3 e5 khan-but8 tiong u7 sia2 chit8-phiN chin tng5 e5 bun5-chiuN kong2, “Chit8-ui7 jiat8-sim e5 bok8-su leng2-to7 e5 hong7-hian3 si7 pi2 tui3 An-tai7-liok8 kau3-khu sou2 u7 e5 Thian-chu2-kau3 kau3-hoe7 e5 hong7-hian3 koh khah choe7.” I kong2, “Lan2 si7 sin3-giong2 e5 chin-sit8 e5 koan2-li2-jin5, chong2-si7 lan2 hou7 chit-e5 sin-kau3 e5 kau3-hoe7 iaN5-koe3 lan2, che si7 chit8 kiaN7 chin kian3-siau3 e5 su7”. Tong-jian5 i e5 i3-su3 si7 beh kek-le7 Thian-chu2-kau3 e5 sin3-tou5 tui3 hong7-hian3 koh khah jiat8-sim. Bo5, goan2 bo5 pah-ban7 e5 pu3-ong, kong2 sit8-chai7 oe7, ti7 goan2 kau3-hoe7, bo5 u7 chit8 e5 u7 chai5-san2 e5 lang5, goan2 e5 hong7-hian3 si7 tui3 chin choe7 peng5-siong5 e5 hoe7-iu2 lai5 e5. 
  U7 chit8-pai2 chit8 e5 toa7 kau3-phai3 e5 goa7-kok soan-to7-kau3-su7 mng7 goa2 kong2, “Kiam2 u7 sim2-mih8 pi3-koat”. I ai3 chai, siaN2-su7 in kau3-phai3 e5 hong7-hian3 teh kiam2 chio2. Goa2 ka7 i kong2, “Bou2-bou2 phok-su7 ah, li2 chiu7-si7 chiong li2 e5 goa7-kok thoan5-to7 hi-seng ti7 u7-sng3 e5 lai7-bin7, li2 kio3 hoe7-iu2 ui7-tioh8 u7-sng3 lai5 hong7-hian3. Jian5-au7 li2 chiong sou2 tit-tioh8 e5 chiN5 chiau3 li2 sou2 khoaN3 choe3 su-iau3 e5 lai5 hun-phoe3. An2-ni choe3 si7 boe7 eng7-tit, li2 boe7 eng7-tit chiong hiah-nih8 iau3-kin2 e5 se3-kai3 thoan5-to7, he7 ti7 u7-sng3 tiong thiu chhut-lai5, he7 ti7 mui2 chit8 e5 lang5 long2 khoaN3 oe7 tioh8 e5 kang2-tai5 teng2. Chin choe7 lam5-lu2 chheng-lian5 siu7 kam2-tong7 beh chi3-goan7 choe3 soan-kau3-su e5 si5, hoe7-chiong3 sou2 su-iau3 e5, peng7 m7 si7 u7-sng3-pio2, chiu7-si7 Seng3 Sin5 e5 kam2-tong7”, i thiaN goa2 kong2 chiah-e5 oe7 liau2-au7, chiu7 chan3-seng5 goa2 sou2 kong2 e5. 
  Goan2 tui3 ta2-loh8 lai5 tit-tioh8 chiah-e5? Kiam2-chhai2 goa2 na7 tui3 li2 kong2, it-teng7 oe7 hou7 li2 u7 pang-chan7 chiah tioh8. 
  Goan2 tit-tioh8 chiah-e5 chiN5, m7 si7 tui3 seng3-chhan, chu5-sian7-chhi7 gi7-hoe7, im-gak8-hoe7, chap8-hoe3 be2-be7 lai5 tit-tioh8 e5. Goa2 m7 si7 hoan2-tui3 chiah-e5 lai5 tit-tioh8 chiN5, in-ui7 hoe7-iu2 bo5 ai3 cho3 chiah-e5 tai7-chi3. Chit8 e5 seng-li2 lang5 teh choe3 i sou2 bo5 ai3 e5 seng-li2, i kiam2 oe7 seng5-kong? Hian7-chai7 goan2 teh chi-chhi5 350 mia5 e5 soan-kau3-su, mui2 ko3-geh8 goan2 tioh8 ai3 u7 2 ban7 khou, na7 bo5, hiah-e5 soan-kau3-su oe7 tu2-tioh8 kan-khou2. ChhiaN2 mng7, lin2 cho3 seng-li2 e5 lang5 u7 kui2 e5 u7 chiah nih8 toa7 e5 chek-jim7 neh? Siat-su2 li2 mui2 ko3-geh8 na7 it-teng7 tioh8 ai3 u7 2 ban7-khou, li2 beh an2-choaN2? Siat-su2 na7 u7 350 mia5 e5 kang-lang5, teh oa2-kho3 li2 lai5 seng-oah8 e5 si5 li2 beh chaiN2-iuN7? Goa2 ai3 ka7 li2 kong2: “Siong7-te3 tek-khak bo5 kou-hu7 lang5, bo5-lun7 goa2 ti7 kok-lai7 a2-si7 kok-goa7, ti7 Eng-kok, O3-tai7-li7-a khui pou3-to7-tai7-hoe7 sou2 su-iau3 e5 kim-chiN5 long2 bo5 khiam3-kheh, chiau3 siong5 tit-tioh8 ia7 chiau3 siong5 chi-chhut”. 
  Hian7-chai7 chhiaN2 ka7 goa2 kong2, “Li2 kiam2 bat tui3 chap8-hoe3 e5 be2-be7 tit-tioh8 2 ban7 khou? Na7-si7 bo5, choe3 hit-e5 su7 u7 sim2-mih8 lou7-eng7? An2-ni goa2 tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 choe3? Tong-jian5 tioh8 oaN7 pat8-khoan2 e5 hong-hoat, chiu7-si7 oe7-thang tit-tioh8 kau3-giah8 e5 kim-chiN5 e5 hong-hoat. Choe7-choe7 lang5 u7 chit-khoan2 e5 siuN7-hoat chiu7-si7, “Kiau-ti7 Bou7-lek8 si2-khi3 e5 si5, Kiau-ti7 Bou7-lek8 e5 Siong7-te3 ia7 si2-khi3.” Chong2-si7 goa2 ai3 kong2 Siong7-te3 boe7 oe7 si2, I2-li7-a e5 Siong7-te3 hian7-chai7 iau2 teh oah8, I oe7 choe3-chhut sou2 su-iau3 e5 sin5-jiah. “Goa2 ka7 li2 kong2, li2 na7 sin3 goa2, li2 kiam2 boe7 khoaN3-kiN3 Siong7-te3 e5 eng5-kng? Sin3 e5 lang5 hoan7-su7 long2 oe7.” 
  Koe3-khi3 30 ni5 ku2 mui2 ni5 goan2 long2 khui soan-kau3-su hoe7-gi7, ki5-kan si7 4 le2-pai3 ku2, u7 5 e5 le2-pai3-jit8. Chu7-hoe7 chit8 jit8 3 pai2, cha2-khi2-si5, e7-tau3-si5, e7-am3-si5, tai7-seng hou7 chham-ka chu7-hoe7 e5 lang5 u7 kok-goa7 thoan5-to7 e5 iN7-siong7 liau2-au7, goan2 chiu7 ku2-heng5 kho3 sin3-sim e5 hong7-hian3, goan2 e5 hoe7-chiong3 chiu7 piau2-si7 ti7 beh lai5 e5 12 ko3-geh8 tiong sou2 pe7-thang hong7-hian3 e5 sou3-bok8. 
